Budalang’i MP Raphael Wanjala was last evening arrested in Kisumu after a dramatic chase from Kakamega. Mr Wanjala was cornered at a Kisumu hotel by flying squad officers. He was accused of allegedly inciting supporters to cause chaos at a function in Budalang’i on Friday. ALSO READ:

